OL,3,CSurrey Police 'requires improvement'
OL,4,Cwhen investigating crime, report finds
OL,6,FAn inspection of Surrey Police has
OL,7,Ffound it 'requires improvement' in
OL,8,Ffour areas.
OL,10,FThis includes investigating crime,
OL,11,Fmanaging fraud, leadership and
OL,12,Fdiversity.
OL,14,FThe force has been rated 'good' at
OL,15,Freducing crime and keeping people safe.
OL,17,FThe Chief Constable of Surrey Police
OL,18,Fsays the report is a "fair assessment"
OL,19,F- adding the force is due to undergo a
OL,20,F"much-needed" organisational
OL,21,Frestructure next month.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
