OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1777546976
OL,3,CSurrey Police 'requires improvement'
OL,4,Cwhen investigating crime, report finds
OL,6,FTim De Meyer said, "I welcome today's
OL,7,FPEEL report and accept its findings.
OL,9,F"The period covered by this inspection
OL,10,Freflects the first two years of our
OL,11,Ffive-year strategy, which prioritises
OL,12,Ffighting crime, protecting people, and
OL,13,Fearning public trust.
OL,15,F"The PEEL report is a fair assessment
OL,16,Fof our progress made so far, and the
OL,17,Fimprovements still required. We are
OL,18,Fgrateful for the acknowledgement of
OL,19,Fcontinued improvement across the force.
OL,26,@nD@TOUqD@AOUwD@AOU
