OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1777546976
OL,3,CSurrey Police 'requires improvement'
OL,4,Cwhen investigating crime, report finds
OL,6,F"The inspection found encouraging
OL,7,Fearly progress under our five year
OL,8,Fplan, reporting how we have maintained
OL,9,Four good record in crime prevention,
OL,10,Fproblem solving, and visible
OL,11,Fneighbourhood policing while
OL,12,Faddressing previous areas of weakness
OL,13,Fsuch as response times and charge
OL,14,Frates.
OL,16,F"On 10 May we will implement our most
OL,17,Fimportant organisational restructure
OL,18,Fin a generation, a much-needed change
OL,19,Fto longstanding structures and
OL,20,Farrangements.
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU
