OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1777546976
OL,3,CSurrey Police 'requires improvement'
OL,4,Cwhen investigating crime, report finds
OL,6,F"This will ensure that we are
OL,7,Fresilient and prepared for the crime
OL,8,Fand policing challenges ahead.
OL,10,F"I am grateful to every officer,
OL,11,Fmember of staff, and volunteer in
OL,12,FSurrey Police for their hard work and
OL,13,Fresilience.
OL,15,F"Together we are determined to serve
OL,16,Fvictims tirelessly, pursue criminals
OL,17,Frelentlessly and cut crime in our
OL,18,Fcounty."
OL,26,@rD@AOUzD@HO]
